{
  "stem": "17135.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- I-- I was confident if I escape and-- and have a civilian jacket, my chances of survival are by far higher than when you go with pajama, because the Germans, when they saw somebody-- even the Poles-- with pajama, they knew it's-- it's an escapee from a concentration camp, and they report him immediately to SS.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we marched-- we're in Reichenbach two days, and then we marched out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And again, the same dilemma, we march several days, and I was totally emaciated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just couldn't really anymore-- and I was on the border of losing my will to survive after so many years.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Behind me was also-- of the group of the-- of the youngsters from the [INAUDIBLE], the [INAUDIBLE] groups.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was, for some reason, was stronger than me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, they-- the-- the number one guarantee for survival is good shoes, and they stole my shoes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had first rate shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They stole my shoes at night when you sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, everybody was out to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I had wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the worst, you know, because before you know it you have all [?wounds?] all over the feet.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew the chance for survival are nil.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and this guy behind me, that was matching behind me, often said, if you don't escape, give me the jacket.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He constantly was nudging me-- nudging me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We arrived at a small town, [INAUDIBLE], near the Czech border, and while we were matching at night, on the main street, on both sides of the street were the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're watching us, making fun of us, and nasty, nasty remarks, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You deserve to die, and look what you've done to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now [INAUDIBLE] suffered, because of you-- all this garbage.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
